    "name": "Scholar (Archaeologist)",
    "type": "npc",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "html": "An archaeologist is a cunning scholar and explorer of ancient texts and ruins. She is knowledgeable in a wide range of fields, as quick with a quip or quotation as with a blade, bolt, or lash. An archaeologist might partner with a medium to placate the spirits of the dead disturbed in her explorations (CR 7), or supply a traveling merchant with exotic relics (CR 8)."
        }
    ],
